_:Neba5d01461754852b0394ab5098131ad <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>RWM has a board of directors chaired by Professor Malcolm Morley OBE. This is the primary mechanism for the governance of RWM, including review of monthly performance reports against the agreed business plan. NDA sanctions funding for RWM.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"the-rwm-board\">The RWM Board</h2>\n\n<p>RWM’s board:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>sets out our strategic direction</li>\n  <li>is responsible for ensuring we observe high standards of corporate governance</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Our Board members are:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>Professor Malcolm Morley OBE (Chair)</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/karen-wheeler\" class=\"govuk-link\">Karen Wheeler CBE (Chief Executive)</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/peter-lock\" class=\"govuk-link\">Peter Lock (Health, Safety, Security, Environment and Quality Director)</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Claes Thegerström (Independent Non-Executive Director)</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Professor Michael Bowman (Independent Non-Executive Director)</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/david-prout\" class=\"govuk-link\">Dr David Prout CB (Independent Non-Executive Director)</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/corhyn-parr\" class=\"govuk-link\">Corhyn Parr (NDA Nominated Non-Executive Director)</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Alan Cumming (NDA Nominated Non-Executive Director)</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"executive-team\">Executive Team</h2>\n\n<p>The RWM board delegates day-to-day management to the executive team, which includes the managing director and other directors. The executive team is accountable for implementing the strategy and plans approved by the board. Its members are:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/karen-wheeler\" class=\"govuk-link\">Karen Wheeler CBE (Chief Executive)</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/john-corderoy\" class=\"govuk-link\">John Corderoy (Technical Director)</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/peter-welch\" class=\"govuk-link\">Peter Welch (Business Services Director)</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/peter-lock\" class=\"govuk-link\">Peter Lock (Health, Safety, Security, Environment and Quality Director)</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/shaun-robarts\" class=\"govuk-link\">Shaun Robarts (Waste Management Director)</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/guy-esnouf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Guy Esnouf (Director of Communications and Stakeholder Engagement)</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/andrew-champ\" class=\"govuk-link\">Andrew Champ (Commercial Director)</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/simon-hughes--2\" class=\"govuk-link\">Simon Hughes (Community Engagement and Siting Director)</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Nicole Westcott (Human Resources and Transformation Director)</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Andy Bevington (Interim GDF Programme Director)</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"rwm-board-meeting-minutes\">RWM Board Meeting Minutes</h2>\n\n<p>We publish board meeting minutes after they have been approved by the board.</p>\n\n<section data-module=\"ga4-link-tracker\" class=\"gem-c-attachment govuk-!-margin-bottom-6\">\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail govuk-!-display-none-print\">\n    <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60b8a27fd3bf7f4bd4662b27/Minutes_of_the_RWM_Board_December_2020_redacted.pdf\">\n        <svg class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image--pdf\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 99 140\">\n  <path d=\"M12,59h9v9h-9v-9ZM30,77v9h39v-9H30ZM30,104h57v-9H30v9ZM30,122h48v-9H30v9ZM12,86h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,122h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,104h9v-9h-9v9ZM30,68h57v-9H30v9ZM35.2,21c-.3-.2-.6-.4-1-.5s-.8-.2-1.3-.2h-2.6v5.5h2.6c.5,0,1,0,1.3-.2s.7-.3,1-.5c.3-.2.5-.5.7-.8s.2-.7.2-1.1h0c0-.5,0-.9-.2-1.2-.2-.3-.4-.6-.7-.8h0ZM52.4,21.9c-.4-.5-1-.9-1.6-1.1-.7-.3-1.5-.4-2.4-.4h-2.7v11.5h2.7c.9,0,1.7-.1,2.4-.4s1.2-.7,1.6-1.1c.4-.5.7-1.1.9-1.7.2-.7.3-1.4.3-2.1v-.7c0-.8,0-1.5-.3-2.1-.2-.6-.5-1.2-.9-1.7h0ZM87,12v27H12V12h75ZM39.8,23c0-.9-.1-1.6-.4-2.4-.3-.7-.7-1.4-1.2-1.9-.5-.5-1.2-1-1.9-1.2-.8-.3-1.6-.5-2.5-.5h-7.2v17.9h3.6v-6h3.2c.9,0,1.8-.1,2.6-.5.8-.3,1.4-.7,2-1.2.5-.5,1-1.2,1.3-1.9.3-.7.5-1.5.5-2.4h0ZM57.4,26c0-1.3-.2-2.6-.5-3.7s-.9-2-1.6-2.8c-.7-.8-1.6-1.4-2.7-1.8-1.1-.4-2.3-.6-3.8-.6h-6.6v17.9h6.6c1.5,0,2.7-.2,3.8-.6,1.1-.4,2-1,2.7-1.8.7-.8,1.3-1.7,1.6-2.8.4-1.1.5-2.3.5-3.7h0ZM72.4,17.1h-12.1v17.9h3.6v-7.5h7.8v-3.3h-7.8v-3.8h8.4s0-3.3,0-3.3Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__details\">\n    <h2 class=\"gem-c-attachment__title\">\n      <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60b8a27fd3bf7f4bd4662b27/Minutes_of_the_RWM_Board_December_2020_redacted.pdf\">RWM Board Minutes December 2020</a>\n</h2>\n\n\n      <p class=\"gem-c-attachment__metadata\"><span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\">224 KB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\">3 pages</span></p>\n\n\n\n\n</div></section>\n\n<section data-module=\"ga4-link-tracker\" class=\"gem-c-attachment govuk-!-margin-bottom-6\">\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail govuk-!